# Introduction

This project uses the AI in Healthcare dataset which contains 5,000 patient records with 20 variables capturing demographic, clinical, and AI-related information. The purpose is to explore whether the AI modelâ€™s confidence relates to recovery time and satisfaction. I use summary statistics and a simple scatterplot to look for any clear patterns.

